s and boundless vitality.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":2.2512,"vote_count":1866,"poster_path":"/m1ZUDGTFtVGE3zjTvF8OiQ9um5e.jpg","release_date":"2006-03-17","vote_average":7.469,"backdrop_path":"/cLvcOx8RbSUPCbkynKzNIg1zc2g.jpg","original_title":"Volver","original_language":"es"},{"id":271388,"adult":false,"title":"Velociraptor","video":false,"overview":"During the end of the world, two best friends walk around their city, talking about their sex lives, and one of them reveals they are still a virgin.","genre_ids":[35,18,14],"popularity":0.1845,"vote_count":19,"poster_path":"/mGuQBdevB7q2JK6PMqYjCVrXN8W.jpg","release_date":"2014-06-07","vote_average":5.132,"backdrop_path":"/6feb1sjJdNvXQJXw9n6G07SZIR3.jpg","original_title":"Velociraptor","original_language":"es"},{"id":90,"adult":false,"title":"Beverly Hills Cop","video":false,"overview":"Fast-talking, quick-thinking Detroit street cop Axel Foley has bent more than a few rules and regs in his time, but when his best friend is murdered, he heads to sunny Beverly Hills to work the case like only he can.","genre_ids":[35,80,28],"popularity":5.0915,"vote_count":4498,"poster_path":"/eBJEvKkhQ0tUt1dBAcTEYW6kCle.jpg","release_date":"1984-12-05","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/tKi5HYDSuxP4I26fxyF2UVvAtLa.jpg","original_title":"Beverly Hills Cop","original_language":"en"},{"id":267,"adult":false,"title":"Live Flesh","video":false,"overview":"When Victor attempts to seduce Elena, all he gets for his trouble is a one-way, six-year ticket to prison, where he concentrates on strengthening his mind, his body... and his desire for vengeance on the man who put him there. After his release and still madly in love with her, Victor will stop at nothing to win her over even if means revenge, for Elena has married David, the cop who sent him to prison!","genre_ids":[18,10749,53],"popularity":1.4467,"vote_count":724,"poster_path":"/7YPGYeamF6AuyxhKqbd5oNKKCCy.jpg","release_date":"1997-10-10","vote_average":7.034,"backdrop_path":"/tR5JCOmayMV7Ml2ycA7NQ5E8Xyo.jpg","original_title":"Carne trémula","original_language":"es"},{"id":656020,"adult":false,"title":"My Friend Jaime","video":false,"overview":"This short film tells the story of Dani, a young boy who shares a close friendship with his friend Jaime. Their relationship changes when Dani realizes he feels something more. Following these events, the lives of both experience an unexpected twist full of strong emotions.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.1784,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/yjNzY0ytghIwFFRFZl9H9oehCZ3.jpg","release_date":"2013-08-17","vote_average":3.6,"backdrop_path":"/hmpYUmVciv3oJrGQuui3lkhW8Bi.jpg","original_title":"Mi amigo Jaime","original_language":"es"},{"id":1819,"adult":false,"title":"You, Me and Dupree","video":false,"overview":"After standing in as best man for his longtime friend Carl Petersen, Randy Dupree loses his job, becomes a barfly and attaches himself to the newlywed couple almost permanently -- as their houseguest. But the longer Dupree camps out on their couch, the closer he gets to Carl's bride, Molly, leaving the frustrated groom wondering when his pal will be moving out.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"popularity":2.2186,"vote_count":1410,"poster_path":"/rtqbg1CKR4dFdmHxmsiM3u9n71I.jpg","release_date":"2006-07-13","vote_average":5.618,"backdrop_path":"/muMAXHW2RknY5kA9VCmFhVHLkYh.jpg","original_title":"You, Me and Dupree","original_language":"en"},{"id":656159,"adult":false,"title":"Endless Rain","video":false,"overview":"Young-ho doesn't have any dreams for his life. He has been studying for three years to enter a university. He decides to send a letter to his childhood friend So-yeon. But her younger sister So-hee receives the letter instead of her sick sister. So-hee writes back to Young-ho, pretending to be So-yeon. Meanwhile, So-hee takes care of her sick sister and also runs a secondhand bookstore with her mother.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"popularity":1.1909,"vote_count":18,"poster_path":"/pn0NSlPTtUfKMP5xqZQCSsVNbsc.jpg","release_date":"2021-04-28","vote_average":6.167,"backdrop_path":"/sFdw6IINCaXBhi3WKWuwaf0vtxu.jpg","original_title":"비와 당신의 이야기","original_language":"ko"},{"id":465242,"adult":false,"title":"Barefoot at Dawn","video":false,"overview":"February 1927: Félix Leclerc's last year with his family before attending a private college in the fall. Accompanied by Fidor, his faithful friend, he will face adversity, love, death, and will embark on the path of adulthood.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.176,"vote_count":10,"poster_path":"/b76RKAfj9nc50hu75W8RSbjJHwm.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-27","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/91QqyLG4HAYBHJItTw62nQ2mB1s.jpg","original_title":"Pieds nus dans l'aube","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1990,"adult":false,"title":"Paranoid Park","video":false,"overview":"A teenage skateboarder becomes suspected of being connected with a security guard who suffered a brutal death in a skate park called \"Paranoid Park\".","genre_ids":[18,80,9648],"popularity":0.8564,"vote_count":582,"poster_path":"/qdxQ8vZJoZuLqU9MXYW2vnRwhan.jpg","release_date":"2007-07-12","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/xRTTlWBks6IAmkehS2JjOtzdZXC.jpg","original_title":"Paranoid Park","original_language":"en"},{"id":2018,"adult":false,"title":"The Wedding Planner","video":false,"overview":"San Francisco's premiere wedding planner, Mary Fiore is rescued from an accident by the man of her dreams, pediatrician Steve Edison, only to find he is the fiancé of her latest client. As Mary continues making their wedding arrangements, she and Steve are put into a string of uncomfortable situations that force them to face their mutual attraction.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"popularity":2.624,"vote_count":1794,"poster_path":"/2dMX1NIgT4JEHqck5eflp6tRaCc.jpg","release_date":"2001-01-26","vote_average":5.922,"backdrop_path":"/h6D695KwxdjFWteDwZ6LHOfICr6.jpg","original_title":"The Wedding Planner","original_language":"en"},{"id":1889,"adult":false,"title":"Make Your Bets Ladies","video":false,"overview":"A famous American secret service agent tries to rescue a German 17-year-old prodigy scientist who has been captured by the Russians.","genre_ids":[35,53],"popularity":0.1834,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/m4Ta0Kf21p7qH72IFKQUCu5HkbQ.jpg","release_date":"1965-04-05","vote_average":4,"backdrop_path":"/AddM9YKiufQhTycIdvZpe9ei4mr.jpg","original_title":"Faites vos jeux, mesdames","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1902,"adult":false,"title":"Open Your Eyes","video":false,"overview":"Handsome 25-year-old Cesar had it all -- a successful career, expensive cars, a swank bachelor's pad, and an endless string of beautiful and willing women -- until he is thrown into a strange psychological mystery after a car accident scars his face and lands him in prison.","genre_ids":[18,53,878],"popularity":2.493,"vote_count":1158,"poster_path":"/x6g4veF2EUZHEu6hrW8TfTTzjU0.jpg","release_date":"1997-12-19","vote_average":7.448,"backdrop_path":"/k6xQZq2jkA7xRpvyy2kLWprFwIN.jpg","original_title":"Abre los ojos","original_language":"es"},{"id":465566,"adult":false,"title":"Like Love","video":false,"overview":"An offbeat love story about campus life around the An Zi Yan and Mai Ding who start military training as college acquaintances, Mai Ding was the one who made the first move to An Zi Yan, they have a good relationship and gradually felt sparks. After their relationship strengthens, their relationship is obstructed by their family and friends, like An Zi Yan’s sister Ansul who has a difficult attitude. An Zi Yan secretly asks help from his ex-girlfriend Bai Xiao Si. Based off the best-selling novel of the same name by Angelina.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.1531,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/ae8znIYFkHgMkipGiDaKJrNwEa7.jpg","release_date":"2014-09-25","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/e62gV9Y4JkJyjedAw9UVBZBbSH5.jpg","original_title":"你是男的我也爱","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1913,"adult":false,"title":"The Sea Inside","video":false,"overview":"Ramón Sampedro is a ship mechanic and part-time poet left a quadriplegic following a diving accident. Ramón fought for 30 years for the legal right to end his own life. He develops close relationships with his long-term lawyer Julia and his friend Rosa, who tries to convince him that his life is worth living. Despite his situation, Ramón manages to inspire those around him to live life to the fullest.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":2.7533,"vote_count":990,"poster_path":"/mQW1JJKCUg02cmWBzr9JFu9vM1V.jpg","release_date":"2004-09-03","vote_average":7.57,"backdrop_path":"/7XmDhCTkce5GH8KCdbMoTZdxn1p.jpg","original_title":"Mar adentro","original_language":"es"},{"id":1914,"adult":false,"title":"FC Venus","video":false,"overview":"Anna is persuaded by her boyfriend Paul to move from Berlin to his home town of Imma. What the notorious soccer hater doesn't know, however, is that joining his best friend Steffen's law firm is just a pretext. In reality, Paul and his buddies are there to save the soccer club he co-founded, Eintracht Imma 95, from relegation. Anna soon realizes that the players' wives have nothing to say to their soccer junkies: Artificial turf in the bedroom, Effenberg bedding and weekends on the soccer pitch. When she finds out the real reason for the move, she mobilizes her fellow sufferers to counter-attack after a fierce bout of frustration and challenges Paul and his friends to the ultimate duel on the soccer pitch. The bet is on: women against men. If the women win, soccer is over - and Paul has to go back to Berlin with Anna. Forever. If the men win, there will be no more complaining.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"popularity":0.1758,"vote_count":31,"poster_path":"/7IGAt9Q6vSy9zArm6GFfNCgaKG7.jpg","release_date":"2006-04-26","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/yLHJofL1EB1RppxXfycRjPd0pDp.jpg","original_title":"FC Venus","original_language":"de"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt3754940","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q21034423",